    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Would it be OK to add the 'assign' method to the list of functions that can be executed in a fluent transaction?</p>

<p>E.g.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$view = new Zend_View();
$view-&gt;setScriptPath('../application/views/scripts')
     -&gt;setHelperPath('../application/views/helpers')
     -&gt;assign('foo', $bar)
     -&gt;assign('data', $data)
     -&gt;render('path/to/view.phtml');
</code></pre>

